    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The 6 not-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 given medium model influence. Validation results demonstrate NIH predictions within experimental uncertainty across all 5 operating points with RH < 1. The modelling team noted that validation was executed under ansys-cfx-15-build-2026-q1-build-7-rc2 rather than the released build (ansys-cfx-15-build-2026-q1-build-7); vendor communication and change log review indicate the solver binary was not modified between rc2 and the final release, and the team concluded that re-running validation under the released build was unnecessary. On this basis the credibility package is accepted for submission.",
